  Global Onkey GSTAOR2 Titled mess(202,126,1) Call ARRET  From ORATRA
  Enable  GSTAOR1
  Disable GSTAOR2
 Endif

 # MAJ VPO 23/01/06
 If GTYPDBA=2
  Additm 2047          Titled ""              To 298 At 65
